import { Button, TextField } from "@material-ui/core";
import React from "react";


export default function DadosEntrega () {

    return (
        <form>
            <TextField 
                id="cep"
                label="CEP"
                type="text"
                variant="outlined"
                margin="normal"
                fullWidth
            />
            <TextField 
                id="endereco"
                label="Endereco"
                type="text"
                variant="outlined"
                margin="normal"
                fullWidth
            />
            <TextField 
                id="senha"
                label="Senha"
                type="password"
                variant="outlined"
                margin="normal"
                fullWidth
            />
            <Button type="submit" variant="contained" color="primary">
                 Cadastrar
            </Button> 
        </form>
    )
}
